191
00:15:13.435 --> 00:15:16.205
You saw that? Do you know Sa Jin Jin?

192
00:15:16.205 --> 00:15:17.975
She was here today.

193
00:15:19.874 --> 00:15:21.544
- Was she? - My goodness.

194
00:15:21.544 --> 00:15:24.815
Her eyes, nose, and mouth all fit in that tiny face.

195
00:15:24.914 --> 00:15:26.914
She was looking for someone.

196
00:15:26.914 --> 00:15:29.654
Whom could she be looking for in this countryside?

197
00:15:30.914 --> 00:15:33.925
Did you buy clothes? It suits you perfectly.

198
00:15:33.925 --> 00:15:36.425
You look so pretty, Soo Hyun.

199
00:15:47.364 --> 00:15:48.504
Hey.

200
00:15:53.845 --> 00:15:56.114
Hey. Ho Sung.

201
00:16:14.894 --> 00:16:18.205
It's Ji Won. Gong Ji Won.

202
00:16:20.465 --> 00:16:21.805
Ji Won.

203
00:17:18.024 --> 00:17:19.165
Pack up.

204
00:17:22.435 --> 00:17:23.564
I said pack up.

205
00:17:28.135 --> 00:17:29.435
You don't have much to pack anyway.

206
00:17:30.175 --> 00:17:31.344
Let's just go.

207
00:17:32.145 --> 00:17:33.145
Get up.

208
00:17:37.244 --> 00:17:39.685
I said get up. We're going home.

209
00:17:39.985 --> 00:17:41.084
This is my home.

210
00:17:43.955 --> 00:17:45.554
Come to your senses, Ho Sung.

211
00:17:47.225 --> 00:17:49.455
No, what was it?

212
00:17:50.225 --> 00:17:51.365
Lee Soo Hyun?

213
00:17:52.324 --> 00:17:53.594
Why are you Lee Soo Hyun?

214
00:17:54.334 --> 00:17:55.834
Why is your name Lee Soo Hyun?

215
00:17:59.764 --> 00:18:01.804
Your love must be really important.

216
00:18:12.915 --> 00:18:14.284
Goodness.

217
00:18:28.264 --> 00:18:32.564
(Sender: Lee Soo Hyun, Receiver: Sa Ho Sung)

218
00:18:32.564 --> 00:18:35.875
(Receiver: Sa Ho Sung)

219
00:18:43.514 --> 00:18:45.885
(Sender: Lee Soo Hyun, Receiver: Sa Ho Sung)

220
00:18:45.885 --> 00:18:48.915
How important was him for you to abandon your own family,

221
00:18:49.314 --> 00:18:52.455
break your own parents' hearts, and change your name?

222
00:18:53.125 --> 00:18:55.854
You should've at least led a good life after making us all suffer.

223
00:18:56.125 --> 00:18:57.725
That was the least you could've done for us.

224
00:18:58.324 --> 00:19:00.465
Did you choose love over family just to go into hiding...

225
00:19:00.465 --> 00:19:02.235
and lead a life like this?

226
00:19:02.965 --> 00:19:04.264
I'm happy.

227
00:19:05.334 --> 00:19:06.334
What?

228
00:19:14.344 --> 00:19:15.445
Fine.

229
00:19:17.115 --> 00:19:19.145
I can clearly see that you're happy.

230
00:19:19.514 --> 00:19:20.615
Let's go now.

231
00:19:21.715 --> 00:19:22.754
Get up.

232
00:19:22.854 --> 00:19:24.524
- I said I won't go. - Why not?

233
00:19:24.524 --> 00:19:25.955
This is my home.

234
00:19:26.824 --> 00:19:28.195
You should go home.

235
00:19:29.625 --> 00:19:30.925
You're crazy.

236
00:19:34.794 --> 00:19:37.735
Let's go. Get up right now. Mom's waiting for you.

237
00:19:37.735 --> 00:19:40.465
Let's hurry home. Mom's waiting.

238
00:19:46.004 --> 00:19:47.175
She's sick.

239
00:19:47.744 --> 00:19:50.415
Because of you, she's sick.

240
00:19:51.244 --> 00:19:53.044
She got sick from waiting for you to come home.

241
00:19:53.645 --> 00:19:55.084
Who are you to make Mom sick?

242
00:19:57.314 --> 00:19:59.554
Die. You should just die.

243
00:20:00.024 --> 00:20:01.955
You should die so that she doesn't have to wait for you.

244
00:20:02.094 --> 00:20:05.195
Do me a favor, and just die. I just want you to die!

245
00:20:05.665 --> 00:20:08.465
I just wish you'd be gone. I want you to disappear from this world.

246
00:20:54.814 --> 00:20:57.784
(Jeong Eun)

247
00:21:08.494 --> 00:21:09.794
The number you have dialed is...

248
00:21:19.034 --> 00:21:20.804
(President Jang Ki Bong)

249
00:21:23.435 --> 00:21:26.044
- Hi. - I got you a meeting for the role.

250
00:21:26.844 --> 00:21:28.774
The day after tomorrow in Sinsa-dong at 7pm.

251
00:21:29.814 --> 00:21:31.844
- You're coming, right? - Of course.

252
00:21:31.844 --> 00:21:33.415
When are you moving into the office?

253
00:21:34.014 --> 00:21:36.054
I'm paying the fee alone until you move in.

254
00:21:36.054 --> 00:21:37.314
I said I'll move in soon.

255
00:21:43.895 --> 00:21:47.494
Gosh, it's winter again which means this year is almost over again.

256
00:21:48.135 --> 00:21:49.135
- Ms. Han, - Yes?

257
00:21:49.135 --> 00:21:50.435
what are you doing for Christmas?

258
00:21:50.735 --> 00:21:52.004
I don't know.

259
00:21:52.564 --> 00:21:54.064
Do you want to hang out with me?

260
00:21:55.205 --> 00:21:57.574
On Christmas? Don't you have a date?

261
00:21:57.804 --> 00:21:59.044
No, I don't.

262
00:21:59.375 --> 00:22:00.544
Why not?

263
00:22:00.544 --> 00:22:03.415
I'm getting married on Christmas.

264
00:22:03.415 --> 00:22:06.084
- What? - I'm getting married on Christmas.

265
00:22:06.544 --> 00:22:07.715
Are you serious?

266
00:22:08.385 --> 00:22:10.485
My gosh, congratulations.

267
00:22:12.054 --> 00:22:16.294
But why are you rushing to get married?

268
00:22:19.494 --> 00:22:21.334
We have everything we need for our marriage.

269
00:22:21.735 --> 00:22:22.764
Sorry?

270
00:22:26.735 --> 00:22:27.774
No way.

271
00:22:29.405 --> 00:22:31.244
Why are you blushing like a kid?

272
00:22:34.104 --> 00:22:36.814
I'm glad you guys have all that you need.

273
00:22:37.715 --> 00:22:38.844
- Ms. Han. - Yes?

274
00:22:39.145 --> 00:22:41.014
Do you want to come to the bridal shop?

275
00:22:41.054 --> 00:22:42.054
Me?

276
00:22:44.014 --> 00:22:46.554
I think you need to get your own dress soon too.

277
00:22:47.324 --> 00:22:48.354
Reum.

278
00:22:48.754 --> 00:22:49.955
Hi.

279
00:22:51.125 --> 00:22:52.264
Get in!

280
00:22:54.965 --> 00:22:57.195
Ji Hye is getting married on Christmas.

281
00:22:57.395 --> 00:22:58.665
- Is that so? - Yes.

282
00:23:00.264 --> 00:23:01.804
Then what are you going to do?

283
00:23:02.205 --> 00:23:05.804
I'll give her a lot of cash for her wedding. She's in my team after all.

284
00:23:05.804 --> 00:23:07.975
What? So we're not hanging out on Christmas?

285
00:23:08.975 --> 00:23:10.115
We're going to.

286
00:23:10.244 --> 00:23:13.915
Is there a Christmas gift you want from me?

287
00:23:14.915 --> 00:23:16.814
- There isn't. - But there is one for me.

288
00:23:17.115 --> 00:23:18.155
What is it?

289
00:23:18.324 --> 00:23:20.685
- A handwritten letter. - A handwritten letter?

290
00:23:21.024 --> 00:23:24.994
A beautiful, handwritten letter you wrote with your heart.

291
00:23:26.794 --> 00:23:28.965
Well, that won't be hard.

292
00:23:29.235 --> 00:23:31.034
I can write you one right away.

293
00:23:31.135 --> 00:23:32.804
I'll write one right now.

294
00:23:34.504 --> 00:23:36.274
Hold on a second.

295
00:23:48.385 --> 00:23:51.354
Merry Christmas. I appreciate your hard work.

296
00:23:57.665 --> 00:23:59.465
I'll put it in here.

297
00:23:59.465 --> 00:24:00.865
Read it later.

298
00:24:02.465 --> 00:24:06.405
My gosh. Is that a handwritten letter?

299
00:24:06.405 --> 00:24:08.104
I've never written one before.

300
00:24:09.875 --> 00:24:10.905
This is fun.

301
00:24:20.514 --> 00:24:22.455
Why did you come here?

302
00:24:22.655 --> 00:24:24.625
I'm going to sleep at my place today.

303
00:24:25.254 --> 00:24:26.324
Reum.

304
00:24:27.024 --> 00:24:28.324
You're so pretty.

305
00:24:31.465 --> 00:24:32.665
Which part?

306
00:24:32.965 --> 00:24:34.195
- Which part? - Yes.

307
00:24:34.534 --> 00:24:35.665
Go home.

308
00:24:43.205 --> 00:24:45.675
I'm not comfortable with you staying there. Go back to your mom's.

309
00:24:47.205 --> 00:24:48.475
What a cool guy.

310
00:24:48.645 --> 00:24:50.344
Stop playing, and get off now. Hurry.

311
00:24:51.044 --> 00:24:52.514
- Get off. - My goodness.

312
00:24:52.544 --> 00:24:54.385
You're scared of staying there too.

313
00:24:54.385 --> 00:24:56.084
When was I scared?

314
00:24:56.084 --> 00:24:58.254
- Close the door, and go inside. - No.

315
00:25:11.534 --> 00:25:12.665
Gosh, you scared me.

316
00:25:12.665 --> 00:25:14.534
Why would your own mother scare you?

317
00:25:15.135 --> 00:25:16.475
Are you feeling guilty or something?

318
00:25:17.534 --> 00:25:18.675
Not at all.

319
00:25:19.804 --> 00:25:20.945
Who was that?

320
00:25:22.274 --> 00:25:25.814
- What do you mean? - The guy you were with downstairs.

321
00:25:29.054 --> 00:25:30.115
My boyfriend.

322
00:25:30.485 --> 00:25:32.284
What? Your boyfriend?

323
00:25:32.284 --> 00:25:34.494
My gosh. Hey, you. Sit down.

324
00:25:34.494 --> 00:25:35.594
What?

325
00:25:36.695 --> 00:25:37.725
What does he do?

326
00:25:38.594 --> 00:25:39.665
He's a doctor.

327
00:25:41.334 --> 00:25:42.635
A doctor?

328
00:25:42.764 --> 00:25:45.004
- How old is he? - We're the same age.

329
00:25:45.004 --> 00:25:47.064
- Where does he live? - I don't know.

330
00:25:47.064 --> 00:25:48.735
- Where did he go to school? - I don't know.

331
00:25:48.735 --> 00:25:50.635
How about his family? How many siblings does he have?

332
00:25:50.635 --> 00:25:53.705
Are his parents alive? What do they do?

333
00:25:53.705 --> 00:25:56.175
I don't know. I didn't ask.

334
00:25:56.175 --> 00:25:57.915
What? You're unbelievable.

335
00:25:57.915 --> 00:26:00.284
Think about your age. How could you not ask him those questions?

336
00:26:00.284 --> 00:26:02.915
These days, whether it's fate or not,

337
00:26:02.915 --> 00:26:06.084
every relationship is built on qualifications.

338
00:26:06.324 --> 00:26:08.254
You must check thoroughly from A to Z.

339
00:26:08.254 --> 00:26:10.254
That's how you'll know whether to marry or break up with him.

340
00:26:12.264 --> 00:26:13.294
Marry him?

341
00:26:16.635 --> 00:26:20.764
When did you decide that you were going to marry Dad?

342
00:26:20.764 --> 00:26:24.104
I decided to get married...

343
00:26:24.104 --> 00:26:25.205
When?

344
00:26:25.205 --> 00:26:28.344
When I was a little out of my mind?

345
00:26:40.455 --> 00:26:42.554
If it's too complicated, think about it tomorrow.

346
00:26:45.564 --> 00:26:46.824
Tomorrow,

347
00:26:48.834 --> 00:26:50.695
it will all be fine.

348
00:27:22.465 --> 00:27:23.695
Sir.

349
00:27:30.104 --> 00:27:32.104
I have something to tell you.

350
00:28:00.965 --> 00:28:04.975
Someone will visit tomorrow to check the boilers. Don't forget.

351
00:28:05.074 --> 00:28:07.875
We need them checked before it gets too cold.

352
00:28:07.875 --> 00:28:09.814
If you just leave them, it could cause trouble.

353
00:28:09.814 --> 00:28:12.485
And I took your parka to the laundry.

354
00:28:12.485 --> 00:28:15.054
Don't forget to bring it.

355
00:28:15.054 --> 00:28:17.784
There is bulgogi on the frying pan ready to be cooked.

356
00:28:17.784 --> 00:28:20.385
I'll wash white clothes with only a little bit of detergent.

357
00:28:20.524 --> 00:28:22.455
That's how you wash them clean.

358
00:28:23.395 --> 00:28:24.794
You're not going far away.

359
00:28:25.195 --> 00:28:27.524
If I leave home for just a while,

360
00:28:27.524 --> 00:28:29.334
it becomes a pigsty.

361
00:28:29.534 --> 00:28:32.705
Gosh, you only know how to make a mess...

362
00:28:32.705 --> 00:28:34.034
and not how to clean them up.

363
00:28:34.034 --> 00:28:36.875
Don't worry. You should go to the hospital and take a rest.

364
00:28:36.875 --> 00:28:38.945
- Think of this as a vacation. - All right.

365
00:28:39.344 --> 00:28:42.514
You're the only one who cares for me.

366
00:28:44.244 --> 00:28:45.744
And by the way,

367
00:28:45.744 --> 00:28:48.685
after I go into surgery tomorrow, don't starve.

368
00:28:48.685 --> 00:28:50.385
Have breakfast, all right?

369
00:28:50.385 --> 00:28:53.054
There's a restaurant that makes good hangover soup.

370
00:28:53.054 --> 00:28:55.494
Gosh, don't worry about me.

371
00:28:55.925 --> 00:28:57.625
I'll take you to the hospital.

372
00:28:57.625 --> 00:28:59.725
You should leave early to avoid rush hour.

373
00:28:59.725 --> 00:29:03.195
No, it's fine. You should go to work.

374
00:29:03.534 --> 00:29:06.665
You're a busy man. Don't mind me. It's fine.

375
00:29:06.665 --> 00:29:08.834
That'll make me feel better.

376
00:29:08.834 --> 00:29:10.334
Don't.

377
00:29:10.334 --> 00:29:12.844
Don't treat me like I have a serious disease.

378
00:29:14.175 --> 00:29:15.915
She'll get well soon.

379
00:29:16.615 --> 00:29:18.844
You need to do something with me after you eat.

380
00:29:30.655 --> 00:29:33.324
- Don't put it over here. - Gosh.

381
00:29:36.365 --> 00:29:38.264
- Did you wash? - What?

382
00:29:43.604 --> 00:29:46.004
I'll do the rest. You should go upstairs first.

383
00:29:46.344 --> 00:29:47.445
- Really? - Yes.

384
00:29:48.215 --> 00:29:49.445
All right.

385
00:30:00.054 --> 00:30:01.254
Stop.

386
00:30:02.955 --> 00:30:05.064
- Mom, I'm going. - Okay.

387
00:30:17.604 --> 00:30:21.244
Oh, my. They're all clean now.

388
00:30:21.244 --> 00:30:23.215
You're always doing the hard work.

389
00:30:23.215 --> 00:30:24.945
It's nothing.

390
00:30:24.945 --> 00:30:28.354
I had to do something after eating such a delicious meal.

391
00:30:28.354 --> 00:30:31.354
I know you're flattering me, but it feels nice.

392
00:30:31.354 --> 00:30:34.324
- It isn't just flattery. Thank you. - All right.

393
00:30:42.735 --> 00:30:43.935
Oh, my.

394
00:30:45.764 --> 00:30:48.004
Hey! Hey!

395
00:31:02.415 --> 00:31:05.254
I knew it.

396
00:31:06.278 --> 00:31:08.678
(Episode 28 will air shortly.)

